WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:02.200
Before I retire

2
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.400
Proposed to Her Majesty the Queen

3
00:00:04.900 --> 00:00:06.666
Make you the head general of the country

4
00:00:06.666 --> 00:00:08.866
The safety of Jian Xuan Kingdom is handed over to you

5
00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:11.400
But the queen refused

6
00:00:11.566 --> 00:00:13.400
Because you are his brother

7
00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.100
You are the only relative

8
00:00:15.133 --> 00:00:17.666
He was worried that there would be too many arguments on the battlefield.

9
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.566
Make you king and give you glory and wealth

10
00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:21.100
Also gave you freedom

11
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.066
You are lying to me.

12
00:00:25.066 --> 00:00:26.200
That's not possible.

13
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:30.500
The queen has the hardest position in the world

14
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:32.466
The predicament he encountered

15
00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:34.833
You just can't imagine

16
00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:36.766
That sister

17
00:00:36.866 --> 00:00:38.966
Did what a sister should do

18
00:00:38.966 --> 00:00:40.500
shelter you from the wind and rain

19
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:42.266
You good brother

20
00:00:42.266 --> 00:00:44.600
Today, he actually rebelled and forced him to abdicate

21
00:00:44.966 --> 00:00:47.166
Let him become the laughing stock of Kyushu

22
00:00:47.666 --> 00:00:50.000
Wolf-hearted thing

23
00:00:50.066 --> 00:00:54.766
I will send you to confess to your ancestors today

24
00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:58.000
Stop

25
00:01:00.766 --> 00:01:02.433
You are not allowed to kill my father

